## Architecture

```
packages/shared    тЖТ IPC contracts, types, Zod schemas. No React, no Node.
packages/ui        тЖТ React component library (@ajh/ui). No app logic.
packages/prompts   тЖТ AI prompt templates. Pure TS, zero deps.
packages/core/ai/data/workers тЖТ Main process only. Never import in renderer.
apps/desktop/src/renderer     тЖТ React UI. No Node.js access.
```

Renderer тЖТ main: `window.api.*` only (via `AppClient` context тЖТ service hooks).

---

## Rules (ESLint-enforced, violations fail CI)

**1. Service hooks only** тАФ never call `window.api.*` in components/routes. Use `@/services`.

**2. i18n adapter** тАФ `import { useTranslation } from '@/lib/i18n'`, not `react-i18next`.

**3. No hardcoded colors** тАФ use `text-brand`, `text-brand-soft`, `bg-brand`, `border-brand`. No `[#RRGGBB]`.

**4. Motion tokens** тАФ `import { transition } from '@/lib/motion'` тЖТ `transition.normal` etc. No inline objects.

**5. UI primitives from `@ajh/ui`** тАФ `Button`, `Input`, `TextArea`, `SelectDropdown`, `ModalShell`,
`ConfirmModal`, `EmptyState`, `ErrorState`, `RowSkeleton`, `GlassCard`, `SettingsSection`, `OptionTile`,
`StreamingText`. `PageShell` from `@/components/layout/PageShell`. No raw `<button>`, `<select>`, `<textarea>`.

**6. Package imports** тАФ `@ajh/ui` directly, not `@/components/ui/*`. Prefer `React.ComponentProps<typeof X>`.

**7. Import order** (auto-fixed by `rtk pnpm lint:fix`) тАФ `node:*` тЖТ external тЖТ `@ajh/*` тЖТ `@/*` тЖТ relative.

**8. Type imports** тАФ `import type` for pure types. ESLint auto-fixes.

**9. Data fetching** тАФ React Query via service hooks only. No `useState + useEffect` for remote data.

**10. Package boundaries** тАФ renderer never imports `@ajh/core`, `@ajh/ai`, `@ajh/data`, `@ajh/workers`.

**11. New IPC capability** тАФ contract тЖТ router тЖТ preload тЖТ service hook тЖТ query key (all 5 steps required).

