## Commit conventions

`feat:` тЖТ minor release ┬╖ `fix:`/`perf:` тЖТ patch ┬╖ `BREAKING CHANGE` footer тЖТ major
`refactor:`, `docs:`, `chore:`, `ci:`, `test:` тЖТ no release. Subject must be lowercase.
